✅ 3. NO — it is not subliminal messaging in the “movie theater hypnosis” sense.

But YES — there are subliminal elements involved.

Subliminal messaging (pop-culture version) is fake.
But subliminal processing is absolutely real.

Humans constantly absorb:
	•	body language
	•	micro gestures
	•	breath rhythm
	•	vocal timbre
	•	eye focus
	•	posture shifts
	•	emotional energy
	•	framing

Even when they are:
	•	distracted
